title: Cake Boss Complete (152 Episodes)
description:
It appears no one seeds Cake Boss episodes any more, so I will put up my whole collection. It is 18.2 gigs total, but you can download what you want. 

I realize Amazon uses a different season breakdown, but these are organized in seasons matching the Wiki entry, so for a detailed listing, go there.
 <a href="
http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_Cake_Boss_episodes" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW">
http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_Cake_Boss_episodes</a>

It is complete through Season 7 Episode 12, EXCEPT FOR FOUR "MISSING EPISODES" below. 

The episodes were gathered from many sources, and are all decent quality for home watching.
They are .mkv format, h264.
The first 5 seasons are 624x352 crf=23.
Seasons 6 and 7 vary a bit, mostly 720x400 or better, crf=22 to 26.
 
All have AAC 2-channel sound.

----------------------------

Download what you want. Enjoy!
